  "title": "Zombie Invasion",
  "description": "Adds a bunch of silly zombie variants to improve mob variety! Now on Modrinth!",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Dm9ig2P.png\" width=\"1583\" height=\"890\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>About</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Zombie Invasion adds 5 new zombie variants with many more in the works.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">They all spawn naturally inside your Minecraft world.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Zombies</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Balloon Zombie | Floats around. You can shoot an arrow at him to pop his balloon!</span></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Floaty Zombie | Hangs around at the beach.</span></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Snowball Zombie | Throws snowballs at anything that moves.</span></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Party Zombie | May throw a party when defeated!</span></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Knight Zombie | Tough armoured zombie</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Zombie ideas? Leave them in the comments!</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Screenshots</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CSLjq3O.png\" width=\"1583\" height=\"890\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1FPe6Yz.png\" width=\"1583\" height=\"890\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rqFQtUm.png\" width=\"1583\" height=\"890\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4kw9gwm.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1126\" height=\"633\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/529GYov.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1126\" height=\"633\" /><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>FAQ</strong></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p>Can I use this in a modpack? |<em>&nbsp;Yes</em></p>\n<p>Can I redistribute this mod (on another website)? |&nbsp;<em>Yes, but be sure to follow the&nbsp;AFL 3.0 Licence.</em></p>\n<p>Fabric? |&nbsp;<em>Maybe</em></p>\n<p>Mcreator? |<em>&nbsp;Yes, but using Mcreator had no impact on the qualty of the mod.</em></p>\n<p>Backport to X version? |&nbsp;<em>No I have a live (sort of)</em></p>\n</div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Credits</strong></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p>https://mcreator.net/about</p>\n</div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>",
